{"word":"δυσηλεγής","slug":"δυσηλεγής","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>δυσηλεγής</b></el> <el>(δυς-ηλεγής, ές) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><el>λέγω</el> <i>to lay asleep</i>\n<br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:confer, compare'>cf.</a> <a href='S:τανηλεγής'><el>τανηλεγής</el></a>\n<p/><i>laying</i> one <i>on a hard bed</i>, of death, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Hesiod'>Hes.</a></b><p/>"}]}